patthana15.15:1.1_0: Hetuṁ micchattaniyataṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nahetu namicchattaniyato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā ….
patthana15.15:2.1_0: Hetuṁ sammattaniyataṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nahetu nasammattaniyato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā ….
patthana15.15:3.1_0: Nahetuṁ aniyataṁ dhammaṁ paccayā nanahetu naaniyato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā ….
